      <title>华为的智能汽车技术为汽车制造商提供了在中国销售的途径</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/huaweis-smart-car-tech-offers-automakers-route-china-sales-2024-04-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华为只用了四年时间就成为智能汽车技术领域的一股力量，在应对贸易制裁对其智能手机业务造成的破坏的同时，还开发了北京车展宠儿的驾驶辅助系统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/huaweis-smart-car-tech-offers-automakers-route-china-sales-2024-04-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 08:04:09 GMT</pubDate>
